": "leaf-blade", "method": "level-up", "level": 44}, {"move": "feather-dance", "method": "level-up", "level": 51}, {"move": "brave-bird", "method": "level-up", "level": 58}]}}], "defaultFormId": 724, "versionEntries": [{"version": "legends-arceus", "text": "The air stored inside the rachises of Decidueye's feathers insulates the Pok\u00e9mon against Hisui's extreme cold. This is firm proof that evolution can be influenced by environment."}, {"version": "moon", "text": "Although basically cool and cautious, when it\u2019s caught by surprise, it\u2019s seized by panic."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "In a tenth of a second, it can nock and fire an arrow quill, piercing an opponent\u2019s weak point before they notice what\u2019s happening."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "It fires arrow quills from its wings with such precision, they can pierce a pebble at distances over a hundred yards."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "As if wielding a bow, it launches the arrow quills hidden among the feathers of its wings. Decidueye\u2019s shots never miss."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "Decidueye can nock and fire an arrow at an enemy in a tenth of a second, so its battles are decided in the blink of an eye."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "It nocks its arrow quills and shoots them at opponents. When it simply can\u2019t afford to miss, it tugs the vine on its head to improve its focus."}], "entryGameVersions": ["legends-arceus", "moon", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun"], "moveGameGroups": ["legends-arceus", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "rowlet"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "dartrix"}, {"stage": 3, "name": "decidueye"}]}